data.description: Welcome to your dream home at 15428 Atwater Dr in the beautiful Community of Quail Meadows, in the city of Brooksville, FL. This stunning property boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a spacious 2,132 square feet of living space. As you enter through the front door, you will be greeted by a bright and airy family room, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing with your loved ones.The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring modern appliances, ample counter space, and plenty of storage for all your cooking needs. Enjoy your meals in the adjacent dining area, which overlooks the backyard and pool area. The open floor plan allows for easy flow between the kitchen, dining, and living areas, making it ideal for hosting gatherings and creating memories with family and friends.The master bedroom is a true retreat, with its own en-suite bathroom and large walk-in closet. The two additional bedrooms are spacious and share a full bathroom which has it's own private door leading out to the pool area, perfect for children or guests. The entire home is filled with natural light, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere.Step outside to your own private oasis, complete with a sparkling pool and screened-in patio. Imagine spending your days lounging by the pool, soaking up the Florida sunshine, or hosting BBQs with friends and family. The backyard is fully fenced, providing privacy and security for you and your loved ones.This property also includes a 2-car attached garage, providing ample space for parking and storage. As. well as a park directly across from the home. Located in a desirable HOA Community, this home is conveniently located near shopping, dining, and entertainment options.Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your forever home.
